      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. This example boasts a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanical maintenance is exhaustive: rod bearings have been replaced, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The chassis retains factory kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. Finished in original Laguna Seca Blue with exceptional paint depth and zero oxidation, this vehicle represents a turn-key solution for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
